39:48.040 --> 39:49.560
that has a totally, like in my case,

39:49.560 --> 39:51.120
it would undoubtedly have a light theme,

39:51.120 --> 39:52.560
and then I would install it on my box

39:52.560 --> 39:53.640
and launch it as a dark theme.

39:53.640 --> 39:56.680
It immediately is different than the picture.

39:56.680 --> 39:58.480
